[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Bass music playing ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "Max Stepanov: Hello! My name is Max, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm a software engineer on the tvOS team.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'm excited to share with you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "a great all-new look of the media playback UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "on Apple TV ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "and what you can do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get the most out of this new functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "available to you as a developer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this session, we will overview the enhancements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the standard playback UI in tvOS 15; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "we will introduce new APIs; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "and finally, we'll discuss best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will help you create a great playback experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's get started.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "AVPlayerViewController provides the standard media playback ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "for users on Apple TV.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "It supports a wide variety of remotes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "including the new Click Wheel remote, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as skipping, scanning, scrubbing functionality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "Siri command, interstitial support, and more.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "We encourage you to start using AVPlayerViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "to allow users to have a similar experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "as with first-party applications on Apple TV.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you haven't yet used AVPlayerViewController -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "or would benefit from a refresher -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "I recommend you to watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Delivering intuitive media playback with AVKit\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "from WWDC 2019, which goes into greater detail ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "on how to incorporate AVPlayerViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "into your application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's overview the enhancements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "we are bringing this year.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "In tvOS 15, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "we entirely redesigned the standard playback UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help viewers stay in the moment ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "through a more consistent, interactive experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "By adding relevant controls and options to the transport bar, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "we improved the discoverability of common playback tasks, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as turning on subtitles or changing audio language.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "The transport bar controls are both universal in nature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as can be application-specific.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with new content tabs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "users can now easily access supporting information -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "like Info or Chapters -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "making inline navigation accessible and discoverable.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "Content tabs can also be used to show related content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here in this example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm viewing a session from last year's WWDC ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "and can browse content recommendations for the session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "without leaving the player.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, we added contextual actions available to users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "during playback.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "Those actions have perfect functionality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "like Skip Intro or Recap.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "To take advantage of the new playback UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "on Apple TV, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application must be linked with tvOS 15 SDK.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "We took this approach to maintain compatibility ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "with any existing applications available to users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "Those applications will get default tvOS 14 playback UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "and functionality.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "By now, you're probably excited to learn ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to adopt some of this new functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your media application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's dive into the new APIs in tvOS 15...",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "...starting with Title View.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "The new Title View displayed just above the transport bar ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "will help users to instantly know what they're watching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "To present the Title View, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll use values for commonIdentifierTitle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "and iTunesMetadataTrackSubtitle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the metadata of the current AVPlayerItem.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "If a media asset does not contain embedded metadata, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you need to augment it, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "use the externalMetadata property of AVPlayerItem.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "When playing live streaming content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "the Title View will also display a badge ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "to indicate the content state to the viewer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "if your application would prefer not to display Title View, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "suppress it by setting the value of new property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "transportBarIncludesTitleView to false.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, let's take a look at the transport bar controls.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "Transport bar controls is a collection of UI elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "sitting right on top of the transport bar scrubber.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "Those controls will help users quickly and intuitively ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=247"
  },
  {
    "text": "find all the playback options ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application may provide.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "Some standard controls -- such as subtitles, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "audio languages, and Picture in Picture -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "are provided by the system.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "As a developer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can extend the list of transport bar controls, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the new property of AVPlayerViewController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "transportBarCustomMenuItems.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "It supports instances of UIAction and UIMenu classes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at an example of using transport bar controls.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, I'm using UIAction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "to let users add the current media item to their Favorites.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "You could also create more advanced arrangements of actions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=289"
  },
  {
    "text": "and present them in a menu, using UIMenu class.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "UIMenus presented by AVPlayerViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "support up to one level of nesting, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the displayInline option.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "For greater detail on using UIMenu and UIAction classes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "I recommend you to watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Modernizing your UI for iOS 13\" from WWDC 2019.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's talk about content tabs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "Content tabs will allow your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "to display complementary information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "or recommendations for more content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "AVPlayerViewController will display the Info tab ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "when a media asset contains embedded metadata ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "or when you supplement external metadata with AVPlayerItem.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, when you supply navigationMarkerGroups ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "with AVPlayerItem, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "AVPlayerViewController will show the Chapters tab.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your application can present additional content tabs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the new property of AVPlayerViewController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "customInfoViewControllers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in tvOS 15, we are deprecating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "the customInfoViewController property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "in favor of the new property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "that allows for multiple view controllers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "To size your content tabs appropriately, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "please specify the height ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "using preferredContentSize property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=375"
  },
  {
    "text": "or define appropriate autolayout constraints.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "When calculating the required height to display content tabs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "the system will size all view controllers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=385"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the height of the tallest content tab.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "When working with multiple content tabs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "size your custom view controllers consistently ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "or verify that the layout is expected at runtime.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=395"
  },
  {
    "text": "And don't forget to set title property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your custom view controller.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "We will use it for the title of the content tab.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "To help you create great-looking content tabs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "this year, we are introducing new content configurations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "in TVUIKit framework: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "TVMediaItemContent Configuration ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "and TVMonogramContent Configuration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at a couple examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how these configurations can be used in your code.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "For instance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "to present a list of media items at 16:9 aspect ratio, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can use the wide cell ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "from TVMediaItem ContentConfiguration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "Set its properties, like image, title, or secondary text.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "You could also configure it to show a badge ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "and playback progress.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you're done, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "assign the contentConfiguration to your collection view cell.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=448"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's that easy.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=451"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you would like to display people or characters ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "associated with the current media content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "use TVMonogramContentConfiguration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information on using content configurations, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=462"
  },
  {
    "text": "I recommend you to watch \"Modern cell configuration\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "from WWDC 2020.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, contextual actions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "Contextual actions allow your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "to display relevant controls during the playback.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "To display contextual actions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "use new contextualActions property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=482"
  },
  {
    "text": "of AVPlayerViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "and provide one or more UIActions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "Typically, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application would want to present contextual actions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "during a relevant section of the content.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "To achieve this, observe the AVPlayer timing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "by adding periodic or boundary time observers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "To hide contextual actions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "reset the property to an empty array.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "Some of you may have already implemented solutions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the skip functionality within your applications.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "With this new API, the user interaction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "with contextual controls is consistent with focus behavior, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "and when used, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will also maintain the Now Playing status ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's talk about some best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "with AVPlayerViewController on tvOS.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "First -- and most important -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "avoid adding extra gestures to the player.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=536"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will interfere with standard playback UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "and most certainly might not work in the future.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=543"
  },
  {
    "text": "Second, supplement missing metadata.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sometimes we have media that doesn't have all the metadata ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=550"
  },
  {
    "text": "baked in with the asset.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=553"
  },
  {
    "text": "In those cases, provide all essential metadata -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "like title, artwork, or description -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the externalMetadata property of AVPlayerItem.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=562"
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you do so, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "we will do the rest to populate Title View and Info tab ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "with all relevant information.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, consider enabling Picture in Picture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your tvOS application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "It will give your users multitasking flexibility, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "allowing for simultaneous video playback ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the ability to swap between full-screen content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Picture in Picture.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get started with Picture in Picture, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "I recommend you to watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=592"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Master Picture in Picture on tvOS\" from WWDC 2020.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "So to recap.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=600"
  },
  {
    "text": "tvOS 15 makes it easier than ever ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "to build great media experiences using standard playback UI.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "The powerful new APIs make AVPlayerViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "more configurable and customizable than ever.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's never been a better time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=615"
  },
  {
    "text": "to adopt it into your applications.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's easy to get started.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information, see additional resources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "for this session in the Developer app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching and enjoy the conference.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=626"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10191/?time=628"
  }
]